1
00:00:06,200 --> 00:00:06,960
What?

2
00:00:08,440 --> 00:00:09,480
Xixi is missing.

3
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:11,540
What happened?

4
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:13,680
Xixi is missing.

5
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:14,480
Don't panic.

6
00:00:14,480 --> 00:00:15,740
Let's call the police.

7
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:20,640
Hello?

8
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:25,280
Okay.

9
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:27,880
Who was it?

10
00:00:28,240 --> 00:00:29,170
It was Chen Jian.

11
00:00:29,680 --> 00:00:30,880
He took Xixi home.

12
00:00:31,240 --> 00:00:33,040
We should still call the police.

13
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:35,280
Chen Jian and I aren't divorced yet.

14
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:36,740
He's still Xixi's father.

15
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:37,720
Besides,

16
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:40,090
he hasn't done anything to hurt us.

17
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:43,680
I have to go home and check.

18
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,280
Okay.

19
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,210
I'll go with you.

20
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,480
Xixi.

21
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,680
Xixi.

22
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,160
Honey.

23
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:28,640
Xixi.

24
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,460
Let go of me, Chen Jian.

25
00:01:32,520 --> 00:01:33,320
Honey.

26
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,720
Chen Jian, where is Xixi?

27
00:01:40,479 --> 00:01:41,479
Xixi is safe.

28
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:44,500
I asked you, where is Xixi?

29
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:54,520
Can I have a word with my wife alone?

30
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,039
If you keep stalling,

31
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,560
Xixi might be in danger.

32
00:02:07,320 --> 00:02:08,120
Okay.

33
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,960
I'll wait for you at the door.

34
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:28,440
Chen Jian,

35
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,180
are you satisfied now?

36
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:39,480
Where is he?

37
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:42,960
Inside.

38
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,480
Damn it!

39
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:48,120
You scared the hell out of me.

40
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,280
If I don't beat this bastard

41
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,240
to a pulp today,

42
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:52,079
he won't know what hit him.

43
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,440
I'm so pissed off.

44
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:55,880
Honey.

45
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,940
I was busy with work before

46
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,490
and had no time to tidy up the house.

47
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,240
I did the housework today and realized

48
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:06,970
that you've worked hard

49
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,080
all these years.

50
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,940
I cooked all these dishes myself.

51
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,920
See if they suit your taste.

52
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,880
I haven't really

53
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:28,640
cooked much

54
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,040
since we got married.

55
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,760
Don't worry.

56
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,760
The food this time

57
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:43,440
is very clean.

58
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,960
You know everything, right?

59
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,360
I know everything too.

60
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,160
Honey,

61
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,320
I was wrong.

62
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,040
I was really wrong.

63
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,159
Please forgive me this once.

64
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:37,320
Give me a chance, okay?

65
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,760
Give you a chance?

66
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,440
Chen Jian.

67
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,480
I'll say this one last time.

68
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,560
Where did you hide Xixi?

69
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,920
I was wrong, Honey.

70
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,120
Will you forgive me?

71
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,320
I was really wrong.

72
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,160
I was wrong.

73
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:13,680
I beg you.

74
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,640
I beg you, Honey.

75
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,360
Where did you hide Xixi?

76
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:39,560
Wen Xin.

77
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:43,640
Chen Jian, what exactly do you want?

78
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,360
Honey,

79
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:45,920
I was wrong.

80
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:48,159
I wanted to harm you, but you saved me and the baby.

81
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:49,520
I know all of this.

82
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,159
I was really wrong. Forgive me this once, Honey.

83
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,880
I beg you, forgive me this once.

84
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,360
Just this once, I beg you.

85
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,080
Please forgive me.

86
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:56,600
Chen Jian, let go.

87
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,640
Believe me, Honey.

88
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,440
I, Chen Jian, will never harm you.

89
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,240
Chen Jian.

90
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,200
Honey.

91
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:09,280
Calm down.

92
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,040
Put the knife down first.

93
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,760
Let's talk this over, okay?

94
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,570
Put it down and listen to me.

95
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:16,920
Chen Jian.

96
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,720
Put the knife down. Put it down.

97
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,480
Chen Jian, come out.

98
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,280
Put the knife down.

99
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,120
Open the door.

100
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,720
Chen Jian, let go.

101
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,640
Let go.

102
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,080
Honey.

103
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:33,640
Wen Xin.

104
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,280
Honey.

105
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:36,080
You scum.

106
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,520
You scum.

107
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:41,680
Wen Xin.

108
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:43,920
Wen Xin.

109
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:45,340
Wen Xin, hang in there.

110
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,700
Wen Xin, you can't die.

111
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:47,600
Honey.

112
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:48,760
Chen Jian.

113
00:06:51,400 --> 00:06:52,280
Can you say

114
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,940
you've never thought about killing Wen Xin?

115
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,610
I'm telling you.

116
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,980
Even if you didn't kill her today,

117
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:01,880
you would have in the near future.

118
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:02,680
No.

119
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,840
I wouldn't.

120
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,880
I already regret killing her.

121
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:15,240
The me from 12 days later

122
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:21,360
is already dying of regret.

123
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,360
So,

124
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:25,440
it was you who killed Wen Xin.

125
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,480
To be precise,

126
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,920
we killed her.

127
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,880
Later, I read all of Wenxin's diaries.

128
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,920
She saved Xixi and me.

129
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,440
But I killed her.

130
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,240
So I hope

131
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,600
you can change fate.

132
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,680
At all costs.

133
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,440
Give Wenxin

134
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,240
a stable life.

135
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,440
Honey.

136
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,680
Wake up.

137
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:11,760
I'm begging you, wake up.

138
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,280
Wake up!

139
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,800
Wake up.

140
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,799
I don't have a chance anymore.

141
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,520
I don't have a chance anymore.

142
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,380
I don't have a chance anymore.

143
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,840
But you still do.

144
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,480
Do I

145
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:01,040
still have a chance?

146
00:09:01,880 --> 00:09:03,720
I don't have a chance anymore.

147
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,810
Honey, you're not dead.

148
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,520
That day,

149
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,880
I really did push

150
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,680
your revolving lantern off the bridge on purpose.

151
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,280
Because I heard a message

152
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,490
from myself twelve days later.

153
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,280
So you want...

154
00:09:42,280 --> 00:09:44,540
I want to help Chen Jian fulfill his wish.

155
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:45,970
I need your help.

156
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,120
It's ready.

157
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:55,600
It looks just like a real knife.

158
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,410
But if pressure is applied,

159
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,560
the blade retracts automatically.

160
00:10:02,640 --> 00:10:03,770
It's not sharpened.

161
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:06,240
You must be careful later.

162
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,320
Thank you.

163
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:22,560
Chen Jian,

164
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,980
don't make any more mistakes.

165
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:27,600
Give Xixi back to me.

166
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,000
Okay.

167
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,140
Xixi is in the bedroom, honey.

168
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,280
Xixi.

169
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:39,660
She's not here?

170
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,800
She's not.

171
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:44,080
Chen Jian, where is Xixi?

172
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:52,760
Impossible.

173
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,200
I brought Xixi back.

174
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,880
Then I went downstairs to buy groceries.

175
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:58,200
She should be sleeping in the room now.

176
00:10:58,200 --> 00:10:59,120
This is impossible.

177
00:10:59,120 --> 00:10:59,920
Chen Jian.

178
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:04,600
Hello?

179
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,840
I heard you're looking for someone.

180
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,600
You took Xixi.

181
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,040
I did.

182
00:11:12,520 --> 00:11:14,520
Okay, don't hurt Xixi.

183
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:16,400
I'll give you whatever you want.

184
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,600
Don't talk nonsense.

185
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,320
Are you trying to set me up again?

186
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,760
If I took Xixi,

187
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,520
what could I ask from you?

188
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:24,560
Wouldn't that be kidnapping?

189
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,360
You're doing this voluntarily.

190
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,920
Okay, whatever you say.

191
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,640
Please tell me where Xixi is.

192
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,160
On your rooftop.

193
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:36,200
Two minutes should be enough for you to get up here.

194
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:37,560
Okay.

195
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,040
Wait for me.

196
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:44,600
You found Xixi?

197
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:46,440
Chen Jian,

198
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:48,240
I'm telling you,

199
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:50,000
if anything happens to Xixi,

200
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:52,040
I'll never let you off.

201
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,840
Rooftop. Strawberry Meow Meow.

202
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:56,360
Let's go.
